### Get all patients
GET http://localhost:3001/api/patients

### Pong
GET http://localhost:3001/api/ping

### Add a valid patient
POST http://localhost:3001/api/patients
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Coffee Cat",
  "dateOfBirth": "2020-01-01",
  "ssn": "010120-123A",
  "gender": "other",
  "occupation": "Professional coffee supervisor"
}

### Invalid gender
POST http://localhost:3001/api/patients
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Dragon Cat",
  "dateOfBirth": "2020-01-01",
  "ssn": "010120-123A",
  "gender": "dragon",
  "occupation": "Castle inspector"
}

